    "description": "在<strong>《RandoMine》</strong>中，你可以扮演四个准半仙，帮助他们偿还因损坏天界酒馆而欠下的债务。<br><br>享受充满生机的细腻像素画面，结交一群奇怪又可爱的人物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/2afdc867620eee96cd4be7f6ba601086.poster.avif?t=1740080269\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/2afdc867620eee96cd4be7f6ba601086.webm?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/2afdc867620eee96cd4be7f6ba601086.mp4?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在遍布宝石、怪物与财富的随机洞穴中，通过挖掘、砍伐、爆破开拓前进。选择自己的一个英雄，每个英雄都有自己独特的技能及优势。创建自己的隧道和竖井，以通达矿脉或挖出隐藏的密室。运用经典的平台跳跃机制来征服既密布陷阱又爬满动物的大厅，顺带收集珍稀的物品。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/1950b736e7667001166b8979b2d55f1c.poster.avif?t=1740080269\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/1950b736e7667001166b8979b2d55f1c.webm?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/1950b736e7667001166b8979b2d55f1c.mp4?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>走访沿途的城镇，花掉辛苦赚来的资源，以永久升级自己的装备，使自己的英雄更具韧性和战力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/fdf31c8dbd8732a622c23e397e979c1c.poster.avif?t=1740080269\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/fdf31c8dbd8732a622c23e397e979c1c.webm?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/fdf31c8dbd8732a622c23e397e979c1c.mp4?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>不过要时刻保持警惕。洞穴中充斥着各种生物，从超大个的青蛙和黄蜂，到长着翅膀的巨型镭射眼珠。大厅走廊中还潜伏着各式各样的陷阱与炮塔，等待着消灭各路冒险者。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/152b8787b38ce2a2e04d0329e8aa919b.poster.avif?t=1740080269\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/152b8787b38ce2a2e04d0329e8aa919b.webm?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/152b8787b38ce2a2e04d0329e8aa919b.mp4?t=1740080269\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>穿越三个不同的生物群落，每一个都有独特类型的敌人及活动，每一个都最终以一个奇特的迷你老怪压阵。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索不断随机重置的关卡，挑战不断，惊喜不止。<br></li><li>解开精心设计的谜题，从而解锁奖励。<br></li><li>赚取升级物品，提升自己队员的各种能力<br></li><li>在每个关卡之前，可选择饰品和咒语来影响自己的游戏。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728420/extras/fc0966e87876c94cb8346ff636944867.avif?t=1740080269\" width=560 height=119 /></span>",
